{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"12cbf61a42","title":"关于“宗派主义”的言论","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cf1e054e8e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"12cbf61a42"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"067a580d9a","name":"蒋念祖"},{"id":"100453cc10","name":"祝德裕"},{"id":"252ebe9ffa","name":"汪涵璋"},{"id":"406296f8f0","name":"袁传织"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"edc00df2f2","name":"刘德昭"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d9e85a76be","type":"title","text":"关于“宗派主义”的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"d906e33bff","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院蒋念祖刘德昭祝德裕汪涵璋袁传织","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"0b2428569d","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党对外打击知识分子，对内打击知识分子党员，有阶级有党就有宗派主义，要消灭宗派主义，就必须消灭阶级消灭党”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"59f3404ede","type":"paragraph","text":"蒋念祖说：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"92fe148f0c","type":"paragraph","text":"“有阶级有党就有宗派主义，所以要消灭宗派主义，就必须要消灭阶级消灭党。党团员一切均有特权。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"ad19586b31","type":"paragraph","text":"刘德昭说：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"4c19ffb7e9","type":"paragraph","text":"党员对问题看法一致，是一鼻孔出气，是互相包庇，是宗派主义。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"4911d4b63f","type":"paragraph","text":"祝德裕说：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"80e7e512de","type":"paragraph","text":"宗派主义是全国普遍现象，反党不等于反人民，不等于反革命，团组织只有象黄继光、罗盛教……等几张王牌，打光了就完蛋了。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"12addae571","type":"paragraph","text":"汪涵璋说：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"74651d8622","type":"paragraph","text":"宗派主义为社会性的等级，这种等级是新社会中孕育着，发展着，是新社会的危机，阶级社会的迥返。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"961db5ee57","type":"paragraph","text":"袁传织说：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"6bab2344f5","type":"paragraph","text":"“党委勾心斗角。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"2b8734b792","type":"paragraph","text":"“团的报告不让同学参加是宗派主义，团员在停课后听两次报告没让同学参加，是政治不公开，对其他青年的歧视，是宗派主义。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"9fc556e2b5","type":"paragraph","text":"边兆祥说：","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"e465ac3f02","type":"paragraph","text":"“我院党委分成三派，一派是以肖英为代表，一派是以陈子谷为代表，比较了解知识分子，一派是以尹凤翔为代表（包括刘颕，王庆华等）最混蛋，把这派赶出学校。”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"edeb9c6391","type":"paragraph","text":"张保发说：","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"822c379909","type":"paragraph","text":"“要求公开档案材料，自己应该知道自己的档案材料。”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"7057dab613","type":"paragraph","text":"“领导上在办公室里片面的听取下级的汇报，下级汇报时把自己的万岁也加进去了。”","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"8da97c8236","type":"paragraph","text":"李霞芬对党员说：","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"5df2b7a3ba","type":"paragraph","text":"“你们为什么不用大字报来鸣和放，这不是有宗派主义情绪吗？党员不出大字报我很反感。”","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"2b8799b886","type":"paragraph","text":"程家庆在整风时向党员说：","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"},{"id":"ae89336464","type":"paragraph","text":"“立即考虑我入团的问题，不发展我入团是否有的人有宗派主义？”","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42"}],"page":{"id":"482e0e00aa","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"12cbf61a42","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}